PropagationPioneersDubai21.name: Propagation Pioneers: Dubai #21
description: The Silk Road was a network of widely scattered trade nodes.
No one knew exactly what was passed on from where and to where.
Pioneers met in the deserts of Las Vegas and Dubai.
Their individual perspectives create a mean global overview.
